										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Chainlink is back in focus after Bridgetower adopted its technology to tokenize the $11 billion DOM X Arizona Copper-Gold Project. The move highlights strong long-term utility, yet price action has remained underwhelming. Like many major coins, LINK has struggled to deliver consistent short-term gains, prompting LINK holders to explore fixed income platforms.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">That is exactly why </span><a href="https://varntix.com/?utm_source=ventureburn&amp;utm_medium=link2404&amp;utm_campaign=news" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Varntix</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is gaining traction fast. The platform offers fixed returns of 20–24% APY, providing investors with predictable income from the start. Demand is rising aggressively, with recent allocations filling within hours and access becoming increasingly limited. As more capital flows into structured income, Varntix is positioning itself as the solution for investors seeking steady returns.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Chainlink Price Prediction Turns Bearish as LINK Stalls Near $9</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Chainlink is currently </span><a href="https://coincodex.com/crypto/chainlink/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400;">trading around $9.24</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and has dropped slightly in the last 24 hours. The overall outlook remains bearish, indicating cautious sentiment. </span></p>
<div id="attachment_200346" style="width: 522px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-200346" class="wp-image-200346 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/prvb26420262.png" alt="" width="512" height="289" /><p id="caption-attachment-200346" class="wp-caption-text">Image Source: Coincodex</p></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Despite this, analysts believe LINK could recover over time. Chainlink price predictions for 2026 range from $13-$20. Some experts believe it could be supported by its role in oracle networks and growing interest in real-world asset integration.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">However, not all investors are willing to wait through market swings. Because of this, many are turning to alternatives that offer fixed income, with returns that are clear and not dependent on price movements.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Varntix Brings Stability to Crypto Income With Fixed Yields</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://varntix.com/?utm_source=ventureburn&amp;utm_medium=link2404&amp;utm_campaign=news" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-200347 aligncenter" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/prvb26420261.png" alt="" width="512" height="287" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">With the crypto market known for sharp ups and downs, many LINK holders are starting to look for more stable ways to earn. What once seemed like an easy way to gain has left a lot of portfolios stuck.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Think of it this way. If you keep $10,000 in a volatile asset that does not move much, your capital may stay the same or even drop in value. But if that same $10,000 is placed in a structured product earning about 20% per year, it could grow steadily. That’s the difference between waiting and actually earning.</span></p>
<p><a href="https://varntix.com/?utm_source=ventureburn&amp;utm_medium=link2404&amp;utm_campaign=news" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Varntix</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is built to solve this problem. It is a digital wealth platform focused on helping users earn fixed returns instead of relying on price changes. In simple terms, it tells traders how much they earn from the start, so there’s no guessing.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Unlike staking or yield farming, where rewards can go up and down with the market, Varntix keeps things stable. Earnings are not affected by sudden price drops, so the value of what is earned stays more consistent.</span></p>
<p><a href="https://varntix.com/?utm_source=ventureburn&amp;utm_medium=link2404&amp;utm_campaign=news" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-200345 aligncenter" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/prvb26420263.png" alt="" width="512" height="86" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Furthermore, Varntix operates like a digital asset treasury, spreading investments across different assets. This helps reduce risk and makes returns more predictable.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Varntix Offers Fixed and Flexible Plans With Predictable Returns</span></h2>
